    • Method Detail

      • findMatchingPremiumReportDueDate

        PremiumReportDueDate findMatchingPremiumReportDueDate(PremiumReportBI newPremiumReportBI)
        This method matches a PremiumReportBI to a PremiumReportDueDate. It is called as soon as a PremiumReportBI comes in. The PremiumReportDueDate that is returned by this method is used to set the 'PremiumReportDueDate' field in the PremiumReportBI, and in turn, this PremiumReportBI is used to set the 'PremiumReportBI' field in the PremiumReportDueDate that is found.
        Parameters:
        newPremiumReportBI - the expired PRDD
        Returns:
        the PremiumReportDueDate that

      • shouldStartFailureToReportDelinquency

        boolean shouldStartFailureToReportDelinquency(PremiumReportDueDate expiredPremiumReportDueDate)
        Should we kick off delinquency? Called by the PremiumReportDueDate Worker Queue when it finds a PRDD with a due date that has passed.
        Parameters:
        expiredPremiumReportDueDate - the expired PRDD
        Returns:
        whether we should kick off delinquency

      • shouldStopFailureToReportDelinquency

        boolean shouldStopFailureToReportDelinquency(PremiumReportBI latePremiumReportBI)
        Should we stop delinquency? Called when a PRBI comes in on a policy that has gone delinquent for non-reporting.
        Parameters:
        latePremiumReportBI - the PRBI that has come in late
        Returns:
        whether we should stop delinquency
